v4.0 (2025-12-10)
* added sentyfonts website/download
* completely reworked 'font style' system so fonts can be in multiple categories
* parse language info for local fonts
* added more 'fonts elsewhere' fonts

v3.0 (2025-04-16)
* added omnibus-type website/download
* added nerdfonts.com website/download
* split code into seperate modules
* move webpage cache to ~/.local/cache/fontporter/
* don't use webpage cache if file older than one hour
* 'set terminal font' now works with more fonts
* handle terminal resize


